OL,3,CEqualities watchdog urges government
OL,4,Cto speed up trans guidance
OL,6,FBritain's equalities watchdog has
OL,7,Furged the government to speed up
OL,8,Fbringing in new guidance on
OL,9,Ftransgender people's use of single sex
OL,10,Fspaces, as it warned some
OL,11,Forganisations are currently using
OL,12,Funlawful practices.
OL,14,FA code of practice, updated in the
OL,15,Fwake of the Supreme Court ruling on
OL,16,Fbiological sex in April, was shared
OL,17,Fwith women and equalities minister
OL,18,FBridget Phillipson more than a month
OL,19,Fago.
