OL,3,CEqualities watchdog urges government
OL,4,Cto speed up trans guidance
OL,6,FThe EHRC's call for expedition of this
OL,7,Fguidance comes as trans rights groups
OL,8,Fannounced on Tuesday they have taken
OL,9,Fthe UK back to the European Court of
OL,10,FHuman Rights (ECHR), over allegations
OL,11,Fit is now failing to comply with a
OL,12,Flandmark equality ruling on
OL,13,Ftransgender rights.
