OL,3,CEqualities watchdog urges government
OL,4,Cto speed up trans guidance
OL,6,FAfter the Supreme Court ruling, which
OL,7,Fsaid the words "woman" and "sex" in
OL,8,Fthe Equality Act 2010 refer to a
OL,9,Fbiological woman and biological sex,
OL,10,Fthe commission issued draft guidance
OL,11,Fon a range of topics, including
OL,12,Ftransgender people's participation in
OL,13,Fsport and use of toilets.
OL,15,FAccording to the draft, a birth
OL,16,Fcertificate could be requested by a
OL,17,Fsports club or hospital if there is
OL,18,F"genuine concern" about what
OL,19,Fbiological sex a person is.
