OL,6,FElsewhere, the draft code said
OL,7,Ftransgender people can be excluded
OL,8,Ffrom competitive sport "when necessary
OL,9,Ffor reasons of safety or fair
OL,10,Fcompetition", and gave an example of
OL,11,Fhow some services might be able to
OL,12,Fadapt to "offer toilets in individual
OL,13,Flockable rooms to be used by both
OL,14,Fsexes".
OL,16,FCommission chairwoman Baroness Kishwer
OL,17,FFalkner said until the new code is
OL,18,Fapproved, some organisations are still
OL,19,Fusing the current one which is
OL,20,Funlawful.
