OL,3,CEqualities watchdog urges government
OL,4,Cto speed up trans guidance
OL,6,FIn a letter to Education Secretary
OL,7,FBridget Phillipson, Baroness Falkner
OL,8,Fasked that the current code be revoked
OL,9,F"as soon as possible now that
OL,10,Fparliament has returned, so that
OL,11,Fcourts, tribunals and duty bearers are
OL,12,Fclear that it is no longer to be
OL,13,Frelied on."
OL,15,FShe insisted the updated code "ought
OL,16,Fto be brought into force as soon as
OL,17,Fpossible", saying this is
OL,18,F"particularly urgent considering the
OL,19,Fspread of misinformation and
OL,20,Fmisleading information on the law
OL,21,Ffollowing the Supreme Court judgment".
