OL,3,CEqualities watchdog urges government
OL,4,Cto speed up trans guidance
OL,6,FOn Tuesday, two trans rights groups:
OL,7,FTrans Advocacy and Complaints
OL,8,FCollective (TACC) and the Trans Exile
OL,9,FNetwork (TEN), announced they had made
OL,10,Fsubmissions to the ECHR regarding the
OL,11,FUK Supreme Court's April judgment and
OL,12,Fallegations it does not comply with a
OL,13,Fprevious ruling enshrining transgender
OL,14,Frights in law.
